The '''PTL-05 Launch Platform''' or '''Proton Torpedo Turret''' was a turret fitted with four [[Proton torpedo/Legends|proton torpedo]] launchers. They could be used to attack from a fairly long range and were especially effective against infantry. Its torpedoes had higher yield than that of the [[Mobile Proton Torpedo Launcher-2a|MPTL-2a]] but had reduced range.

